---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<!-- Uncomment navbar link when team bios are finalized -->
<Layout title="About Explore China" lang="en" alternateHref="/zh/about" alternateLabel="中文" minimalNav={true} darkNav={true}>
  <section class="section card tone-sand" style="padding:34px;">
    <p class="pill">About</p>
    <h1 style="font-size:clamp(36px,5vw,64px); margin-top:10px;">About Explore China</h1>
  </section>

  <section class="section" style="padding: 3rem 2rem 4rem;">
    <h2 style="font-size:clamp(22px,3.5vw,36px); font-weight:700; font-family:var(--font-display); line-height:1.2; margin-bottom:1rem;">Honestly, we just wanted to share something that changed us.</h2>
    <p class="muted" style="max-width:680px; font-size:18px; line-height:1.75;">We're international students who discovered that living somewhere — really living there — opens up a version of the world you didn't know existed. That feeling is what started this. Three years, 80+ students from the UK to China, and it's still the whole point.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="section card tone-blue">
    <h2 class="section-title">The team</h2>
    <div class="grid cols-3">
      <article class="card" style="background:#fff;"><p class="label">Member</p><h3>Name 01</h3><p class="muted">One-line profile will be confirmed.</p></article>
      <article class="card" style="background:#fff;"><p class="label">Member</p><h3>Name 02</h3><p class="muted">One-line profile will be confirmed.</p></article>
      <article class="card" style="background:#fff;"><p class="label">Member</p><h3>Name 03</h3><p class="muted">One-line profile will be confirmed.</p></article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section card tone-rose">
    <h2 class="section-title">Why we built this</h2>
    <p class="muted">A short narrative of the project motivation will be finalized in the next content round.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="section card" style="margin-bottom:36px;">
    <h2 class="section-title">Contact</h2>
    <p class="muted">Email: contact details to be announced</p>
    <p class="muted">Instagram: account details to be announced</p>
    <p class="muted">WeChat: account details to be announced</p>
  </section>
</Layout>
